Final_Rank_by_Avg_Vi_1.label: Final_Rank_by_Avg_Visits_per_day_Number
Final_Rank_by_Avg_Vi_1.query: Visit = load "${App.Datasets.CG_Visit5_tp.FullyQualifiedName}"; Visit_A = filter Visit by 'Status' in ["Completed","Abandonded"]; Visit_B = filter Visit by 'Status' == "Completed"; Visit_C = filter Visit by 'ActualVisitEndTime_sec_epoch' is not null; Visit_result = group Visit_A by 'Visitor_UniqueUserName' full, Visit_B by 'Visitor_UniqueUserName' full, Visit_C by 'Visitor_UniqueUserName'; Visit_result = foreach Visit_result generate  Visit_C.'Visitor_UniqueUserName' as 'Visitor_UniqueUserName',  first(Visit_C.'Visitor_SmallPhotoUrl') as 'Rep_Pic', count(Visit_B)/count(Visit_A) as 'Percent_of_Successful_visits',  count(Visit_B) as 'Number_of_Completed_Visits',  count(Visit_A) as 'Total_Number_of_Completed_n_Abandonded', avg(Visit_C.'ActualVisitDuration') as 'avg_ActualVisitDuration', count(Visit_C) as 'Number_of_Visits', unique(Visit_C.'ActualVisitStartTime_YearMonthDay') as 'unique_ActualVisitStartTime_YearMonthDay', count(Visit_C) / unique(Visit_C.'ActualVisitStartTime_YearMonthDay') as 'avg_Number_of_Visits_per_Day'; Visit_result = group Visit_result by 'Visitor_UniqueUserName'; Visit_result = foreach Visit_result generate  'Visitor_UniqueUserName' as 'Visitor_UniqueUserName', first('Rep_Pic') as 'Rep_Pic', avg('avg_Number_of_Visits_per_Day') as 'avg_Number_of_Visits_per_Day', dense_rank() over([..] partition by all order by avg('avg_Number_of_Visits_per_Day') desc) as 'Owner_Rank', avg('avg_Number_of_Visits_per_Day') as 'Value', avg(sum('avg_Number_of_Visits_per_Day')) over ([..] partition by all) as 'avg_All_Owners'; fake = group Visit by 'Visitor_UniqueUserName';      fake = foreach fake generate "{{cell(Visitor_UniqueUserNa_1.selection,0,"Visitor_UniqueUserName").asString()}}" as 'Visitor_UniqueUserName', 0  as 'Owner_Rank', 0 as 'Value', 0 as 'avg_All_Owners';      result_final = union Visit_result,fake;      result_final = filter result_final by 'Visitor_UniqueUserName' == "{{cell(Visitor_UniqueUserNa_1.selection,0,"Visitor_UniqueUserName").asString()}}";      result_final = group result_final by 'Visitor_UniqueUserName';      result_final = foreach result_final generate 'Visitor_UniqueUserName' as 'Visitor_UniqueUserName', case when sum('Owner_Rank') == 0 then "NA" else number_to_string(sum('Owner_Rank'),"#,###") end as 'Owner_Rank', sum('Value') as 'Value of Selected_Owner', round(sum('avg_All_Owners'),2) as 'avg_All_Owners_Visits_per_Day', case when sum('Value') == 0 then "rgb(168, 183, 199)" when sum('Value') >= sum('avg_All_Owners') then       "rgb(8, 161, 50)" else "rgb(232,67,64)" end as 'Color_Top_Bottom';

Test_Route_Complianc_1.label: Test_Route_Compliance
Test_Route_Complianc_1.query: d = load "${App.Datasets.CG_Visit5_tp.FullyQualifiedName}"; d = filter d by 'Visitor_UniqueUserName' =="{{cell(Visitor_UniqueUserNa_1.selection,0,"Visitor_UniqueUserName").asObject()}}"; d = filter d by date('PlannedVisitStartTime_Year', 'PlannedVisitStartTime_Month', 'PlannedVisitStartTime_Day') in [.."1 day ago"]; d = filter d by {{row(Actual_Start_Time_1.selection, [0], ["min", "max"]).asDateRange("date(PlannedVisitStartTime_Year, PlannedVisitStartTime_Month, PlannedVisitStartTime_Day)")}}; c = filter d by Status =="Completed"; result = cogroup c by ('PlannedVisitStartTime_Year','PlannedVisitStartTime_Week') full, d by ('PlannedVisitStartTime_Year','PlannedVisitStartTime_Week'); result = foreach result generate count(c)/count(d) as 'Route_Compliance',  coalesce(c.'PlannedVisitStartTime_Year',d.'PlannedVisitStartTime_Year')+"~~~"+coalesce(c.'PlannedVisitStartTime_Week',d.'PlannedVisitStartTime_Week') as 'PlannedVisitStartTime_Year~~~PlannedVisitStartTime_Week';
